
Task
Century number.
The 20th century began in 1901 and ended in 2000. The 1st century began in the 1st year and ended in the 100th year.
Find the century number for the given year.
Write a function named century that takes a positive integer year (year) as an argument and returns the century number.
Examples:
â€¢ century (1901) should return 20;
â€¢ century (2000) should return 20.

Solution
function century (year) {
return Math.ceil (year / 100);
}
